WEBVTT

00:15:58.604 --> 00:16:04.269
and released a cloud of milk
that enveloped her head like smoke.

00:16:04.293 --> 00:16:07.399
Somehow, this baby bottle-nosed dolphin

00:16:07.423 --> 00:16:11.712
got the idea of using milk
to represent smoke.

00:16:12.211 --> 00:16:15.559
When human beings use one thing
to represent another,

00:16:15.583 --> 00:16:17.608
we call that art.

00:16:17.632 --> 00:16:19.655
(Laughter)

00:16:19.679 --> 00:16:21.210
The things that make us human

00:16:21.234 --> 00:16:24.314
are not the things
that we think make us human.

00:16:24.781 --> 00:16:27.105
What makes us human is that,

00:16:27.129 --> 00:16:30.265
of all these things that our minds
and their minds have,